'''天主教巴菲亞教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Bafiensis}}；{{lang-fr|Diocèse de Bafia}}）是[[喀麥隆|喀麥隆]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教雅溫德總教區|雅溫德總教區]]。

'''巴菲亞宗座監牧區'''於1965年7月6日成立<ref>{{cite web |title=YAUNDENSIS (BAFIENSIS) |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19650706_bafiensis.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2020-05-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200521101758/https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19650706_bafiensis.html |archivedate=2020-05-21 |language=la |date=1965-07-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1968年1月11日升為教區<ref>{{cite web |title=BAFIANAE* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19680111_bafianae.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2020-05-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200521101912/https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19680111_bafianae.html |archivedate=2020-05-21 |language=la |date=1968-01-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

教區位於[[中部區_(喀麥隆)|中部區]]西部[[姆巴姆-伊努布省|姆巴姆-伊努布省]]，2012年時有239,572名教友（佔轄區總人口54.0%）、27個[[堂區|堂區]]和41名[[司鐸|司鐸]]。現任教區主教為{{link-fr|厄瑪奴耳·達西-尤方|Emmanuel Dassi Youfang}}<ref name="Vatican20200513">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 13.05.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/05/13/200513b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-05-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200520165923/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/05/13/200513b.html |archivedate=2020-05-20 |language=en |date=2020-05-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

